#lem: mitum[divine weapon]; a[arm]; il[raise]; du[perfect]
#etcsl: line-id=62

63. {ŋiš}tukul-a dub₃ bad-ba₉-re₆ ba-ab-du₇-u₃
#lem: tukul[weapon]; dub[knee]; bad[open]; du[perfect]
#etcsl: line-id=63

64. ti sud {ŋiš}pan si sa₂-e-de₃ ba-ab-du₇-u₃
#lem: ti[arrow]; sud[distant]; pana[bow]; si[horn]; sa[equal]; du[perfect]
#etcsl: line-id=64

65. {ŋiš}ilar {kuš}gur₂₁!(TUM){ur₃}-ra zag keše₂-ra₂-a ba-ab-du₇-u₃
